AS Kigali vs Gasogi United

AS Kigali 2-1 Gasogi United

Uko umukino uri kugenda

Umwanditsi

: Eric Tony Ukurikiyimfura

Amafoto

16:52

AS Kigali itsinze umukino ubanza

Ibitego bya Cyitegetse Bogard na Bishira Latif bishije AS Kigali gutsinda Gasogi United ibitego 2-1 mu mukino ubanza wa 1/4 waberaga kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo.

Undi mukino wabaye uyu munsi, Etincelles FC yatsinzwe na Police FC ibitego 2-0.



Tubashimire mwese twabanye uyu munsi, tuzasubire ejo ku mukino uzahuza Rayon Sports na Gicumbi FC saa 15:00 hano kuri Stade ya Kigali. Intare FC zizaba zakiriye Kiyovu Sports ku Kicukiro.

16:48

Umukino urarangiye: AS Kigali yegukanye intsinzi

90+1' Gusimbuza kwa Gasogi United

Irakoze Gabriel asimbuwe na Habimana Noel ku ruhande rwa Gasogi United. AS Kigali ikomeje gushaka uburyo irya iminota.

16:46

90' Iminota y'inyongera

Umusifuzi wa kane yerekanye iminota itatu y'inyongera.

16:42

85' Igitego cya kabiri AS Kigali

Bishira Latif atsindiye AS Kigali igitego cya kabiri ku mupira ateresheje umutwe. Nova Bayama ni we umupira uturutseho ubwo yahanaga ikosa.

78' Ikarita y'umuhondo

16:32

74' Coup-franc ya AS Kigali

16:23

67' Umukino uhagaze gato

Abaganga ku mpande zombi bagiye mu kibuga kuvura Mossi na Bertin.

16:19

60' Igitego cya AS Kigali

16:02

Igice cya kabiri kiratangiye

43' Gusatira kwa AS Kigali

Niyomugabo Jean Claude ahinduye umupira mwiza imbere y'izamu rya Gasogi United, Twagirimana Fulgence awushyira muri koruneri itewe na Ngama Emmanuel, Nsabimana Eric ashyizeho umutwe umupira uca hejuru y'izamu.

15:42

41' Gusatira kwa Gasogi United

Niyonkuru Amani ateye umupira w'umuterekano uvuye muri koruneri, ukurwamo mu buryo bugoranye na Bate Shamiru uhise utabarwa na bagenzi be bawutera imbere bashaka Ndarusanze Jean Claude ariko na we awutangwa na Kazindu Guy.

15:38

38' Ikarita y'umuhondo

Ntamuhanga Tumaini Tity wa AS Kigali ahawe ikarita y'umuhondo nyuma yo gukinira nabi Dusange Bertin mu kibuga hagati. Uyu mukinnyi wa Gasogi United uri gucumbagira, agiye kuvurirwa hanze.

15:31

31' Igitego cyanzwe

Kazindu Bahati Guy akiniye nabi rutahizamu wa AS Kigali hafi n'urubuga rw'amahina. Ikosa rihanwe na Ngama Emmanuel umupira utsindwa na Ndarusanze Jean Claude ariko umusifuzi wo ku ruhande avuga ko habayeho kurarira

15:29

29' AS Kigali yabuze aho imenera

Kugeza ubu nta mupira ugana mu izamu AS Kigali itara mu izamu rya Gasogi United, Ngama Emmanuel na bagenzi be bakomeje gutera imipira ya kure ariko ikanyura hejuru y'izamu.

15:27

27' Gasogi ikomeje gusatira

15:25

24' Igitego cya Gasogi United

Rugamba Jean Baptiste afunguye amazamu ku gitego atsinze ku mupira w'umuterekano wari umaze guterwa na Twagirimana Fulgence bakunze kwita Makenzi.

15:17

17' Coup-franc ya Gasogi United

Rugamba Jean Baptiste ateye umupira ukomeye ahana ikosa ryakozwe na Marc Govin, umupira uramutenguha uca hejuru gato y'izamu rya AS Kigali.

15:16

16' Ikarita y'umuhondo

Nshimiyimana Marc Govin ahawe ikarita y'umuhondo nyuma yo gukora umupira wari utewe na Bertin n'ukuboko, awubuza kugera ku wundi mukinnyi wa Gasogi United.

15:15

13' Gasogi United ihushije igitego cyabazwe

Niyonkuru Amani akinannye neza na Dusange Bertin winjiye mu rubuga rw'amahina, asubiza umupira inyuma kuri Amani uteye adahagaritse umupira ufatwa na Bate Shamiru ubanje kuryama. Bwari uburyio bwiza kuri Gasogi United.

15:06

6' Coup-franc ya AS Kigali

Ngama Emmanuel ateye mu izamu ahana ikosa rikozwe na Byumvuhore Tresor umupira ufatwa neza n'umunyezamu wa Gasogi United, Cuzuzo Aime Gael.

15:03

3' Amakipe yombi ari gukina umukino mwiza

AS kigali na Gasogi United atangiye akina umupira mwiza wo hasi, aho abakinnyi bari guhererekanya, ikipe imwe ikagorwa no kwambura indi umupira.

15:00

Umukino uratangiye

Gasogi itangiye isatira bikomeye AS Kigali, ibona koruneri ku isegonda rya 35, ariko ntacyo itanze. Umukino wasifuwe na Ruzindana Nsoro.

14:57

Ibigwi by'amakipe yombi mu gikombe cy'Amahoro

Gasogi United iri gukina igikombe cy'Amahoro ku nshuro ya kabiri ariko mu mwaka ushize yitwaga Unity FC de Gasogi aho yasezerewe na Bugesera FC muri 1/8 mu gihe AS Kigali yo yakuwemo na Mukura Victory Sports muri 1/4.

Gasogi United ni imwe mu makipe abiri yo mu cyiciro cya kabiri asigaye mu gikombe cy'Amahoro uyu mwaka, hamwe na Intare FC.

AS Kigali yatwaye iri rushanwa mu 2013 itsinze AS Muhanga ku mukino wa nyuma, ihagararira u Rwanda muri CAF Confederation Cup ya 2014.

14:50

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo

Tubahaye ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo hagiye kubera umukino ubanza wa 1/4 cy'igikombe cy'Amahoro hagati ya AS Kigali na Gasogi United.

AS Kigali yageze muri iki cyiciro nyuma yo gusezerera APR FC mu gihe Gasogi United yakuyemo Rwamagana City FC.
